What is the best way to embed an explanation of Einstein's theory of relativity into an HTML page using PHP? 
[Mark down code]
First, create a new PHP file and save it as "relativity.php". Then, insert the following code:
```php
<?php
$explanation = "Insert your explanation of Einstein's theory of relativity here";
echo "<div class='relativity'>$explanation</div>";
?>
```
Next, add the following code to your HTML page where you want the explanation to appear:
```html
<div class="explanation">
<?php include 'relativity.php'; ?>
</div>
```
Finally, style the "relativity" class in your CSS file to format the explanation as desired:
```css
.relativity {
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  color: #333;
}
```
